{
  "text": "We compare NMT with with MASS and a strong TGen based delexicalized model proposed by [CITATION_1] . From the results in Table 10 , we see that all the models exhibit low SER, as expected. Our model outperforms the best baseline by 5 BLEU points, pointing to the applicability of our approach even in the case of delexicalized NLG. We leave the combination of this model with a lexicalizer component for future work.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "204737903"
